reviewText: My son loves this low budget movie.  Glad I found it.  works perfectly.
This is a pretty unlikely premise but the movie was fun to watch and the actors did a great job.

Kids world was a movie that i had never heard of and i thougt it was going to be the worst movie ever created, but i thought that,when i first saw it ,it was pretty good. Although it was the sound in the movie that could have been better. But i still think the story was a 3 out of 5 because some scenes did not make any sense like the hands pulling the kids into the hole. I give Kid's World a 4 out of 5
